---
const inputClass = "w-full bg-surface-card border border-hairline-strong rounded-[8px] px-4 py-3 text-[15px] text-ink focus:border-ink focus:border-2 focus:outline-none transition-all";
const labelClass = "block text-[14px] font-medium text-ink mb-2";
---

<div class="bg-surface-card border border-hairline rounded-[16px] p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 shadow-sm relative z-10">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center mb-6">
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-ink font-light mb-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-link mr-2 text-muted-soft"></i> Integrasi Moodle</h2>
      <p class="text-body text-[14px]">Atur kredensial koneksi dan sinkronisasi data kelas.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="moodle-test-status" class="hidden mt-4 md:mt-0 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[12px] font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase border"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex border-b border-hairline mb-8">
    <button type="button" class="tab-btn-moodle flex-1 pb-3 border-b-2 border-primary text-ink font-medium transition-colors" data-target="tab-config">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-gear mr-2"></i> 1. Konfigurasi API
    </button>
    <button type="button" class="tab-btn-moodle flex-1 pb-3 border-b-2 border-transparent text-muted-soft hover:text-ink transition-colors disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed" data-target="tab-sync" id="tab-btn-sync" disabled title="Lakukan uji koneksi terlebih dahulu">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-arrow-down mr-2"></i> 2. Sinkronisasi (Chunk)
    </button>
  </div>

  <div id="tab-config" class="tab-pane-moodle space-y-10">
    <form id="moodle-config-form" class="space-y-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-10">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-medium text-ink">Titik Akses Utama</h3>
          <div>
            <label class={labelClass}>REST Endpoint Moodle</label>
            <input type="url" id="moodle_rest_endpoint" class={inputClass} placeholder="https://lms.sekolah.sch.id/webservice/rest/server.php" required>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class={labelClass}>Token Autentikasi</label>
            <input type="password" id="moodle_token" class={inputClass} placeholder="Masukkan token REST service">
            <p id="moodle_token_hint" class="text-[13px] text-muted-soft mt-2 hidden">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-check text-semantic-success mr-1"></i> Token tersimpan: <span id="moodle_token_masked" class="font-mono bg-surface-strong px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md"></span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[12px] text-muted-soft leading-relaxed">
            Gunakan tombol <b>Uji Koneksi REST</b> di bawah untuk mengecek endpoint/token tanpa menyimpan. Tombol <b>Simpan</b> akan mengetes koneksi terlebih dahulu sebelum menulis ke database.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[18px] font-medium text-ink">Pemetaan Kelas (Course ID)</h3>
              <p class="text-[14px] text-body mt-1">Relasi ID internal Moodle terhadap entitas kelas. Course baru seperti 9A bisa diambil otomatis dari API Moodle.</p>
            </div>
            <button type="button" id="btn-sync-course-map" class="shrink-0 bg-surface-card text-ink border border-hairline-strong rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-[13px] font-semibold hover:bg-surface-strong transition-colors">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-arrows-rotate mr-1"></i> Sync Course
            </button>
          </div>
          <div id="course-map-summary" class="hidden text-[12px] text-muted-soft bg-canvas-soft border border-hairline rounded-xl px-3 py-2"></div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4" id="course-map-container"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-8 border-t border-hairline flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-end gap-3">
        <button type="button" id="btn-test-moodle" class="w-full md:w-auto bg-transparent text-ink border border-hairline-strong rounded-full px-8 py-3 text-[15px] font-medium hover:bg-surface-strong transition-colors">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-network-wired mr-2"></i> Uji Koneksi REST
        </button>
        <button type="submit" id="btn-save-moodle" class="w-full md:w-auto bg-primary text-white rounded-full px-8 py-3 text-[15px] font-medium hover:bg-primary-active transition-colors shadow-sm">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk mr-2"></i> Simpan Konfigurasi
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>

  <div id="tab-sync" class="tab-pane-moodle hidden space-y-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

      <button type="button" id="btn-open-chunk-modal" class="group bg-surface-card border border-hairline hover:border-primary p-6 rounded-[16px] text-left transition-all shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-canvas-soft rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-ink group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-database text-xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-medium text-ink mb-2">Lihat Chunk di Database</h3>
        <p class="text-[14px] text-body">Tinjau semua potongan materi (Manual & Moodle) yang siap dibaca oleh AI.</p>
      </button>

      <button type="button" id="btn-open-sync-wizard" class="group bg-surface-card border border-hairline hover:border-primary p-6 rounded-[16px] text-left transition-all shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#a7e5d3] to-transparent opacity-40 rounded-full blur-2xl transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-60"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-canvas-soft rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-ink group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-plug-circle-bolt text-xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-medium text-ink mb-2">Koneksikan Materi Moodle</h3>
          <p class="text-[14px] text-body">Pratinjau materi LMS dan ekstrak teksnya menjadi chunk RAG baru.</p>
        </div>
      </button>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="modal-view-chunks" class="fixed inset-0 bg-ink/40 backdrop-blur-sm z-[60] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
  <div class="bg-surface-card w-full max-w-[1000px] h-[80vh] rounded-[24px] shadow-lg flex flex-col overflow-hidden transform scale-95 opacity-0 transition-all duration-300">
    <div class="p-6 border-b border-hairline flex justify-between items-center bg-canvas-soft">
      <h3 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-ink"><i class="fa-solid fa-database mr-2"></i> Database Chunk RAG</h3>
      <button type="button" class="btn-close-modal text-muted hover:text-ink text-xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></button>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-6 bg-canvas">
      <div id="chunks-loading" class="text-center py-10 text-muted-soft hidden"><i class="fa-solid fa-spinner fa-spin text-2xl"></i><p class="mt-2">Memuat data chunk...</p></div>

      <table class="w-full text-[14px] text-left border-collapse table-fixed bg-surface-card rounded-lg overflow-hidden hidden" id="chunks-table">
        <thead class="bg-surface-strong text-ink border-b border-hairline-strong">
          <tr><th class="py-3 px-4 w-24">Sumber</th><th class="py-3 px-4 w-48">Topik</th><th class="py-3 px-4">Teks (Preview)</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="chunks-table-body" class="divide-y divide-hairline text-body"></tbody>
      </table>
      <div id="chunks-empty" class="hidden text-center py-16 text-muted-soft">Belum ada chunk di database.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="modal-sync-wizard" class="fixed inset-0 bg-ink/50 backdrop-blur-sm z-[60] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-0 md:p-6">
  <div class="bg-surface-card w-full h-full md:h-[90vh] md:max-w-[1200px] md:rounded-[24px] shadow-2xl flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden transform scale-95 opacity-0 transition-all duration-300">

    <div class="p-6 border-b border-hairline flex justify-between items-center bg-canvas-soft shrink-0">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-ink">Koneksikan Materi LMS</h3>
        <p class="text-[14px] text-muted-soft mt-1" id="wizard-subtitle">Step 1: Pilih & Review Materi HTML</p>
      </div>
      <button type="button" class="btn-close-modal text-muted hover:text-ink text-xl w-10 h-10 bg-surface-strong rounded-full"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></button>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 overflow-hidden relative flex">

      <div id="wizard-step-1" class="w-full h-full overflow-y-auto p-6 bg-canvas">
        <div id="materials-loading" class="text-center py-20 text-muted-soft"><i class="fa-solid fa-spinner fa-spin text-3xl"></i><p class="mt-4 text-[15px]">Menyisir semua materi kelas...</p></div>

        <div id="materials-empty" class="hidden text-center py-24 text-muted-soft flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-surface-strong rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-4"><i class="fa-solid fa-folder-open"></i></div>
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-medium text-ink mb-1">Kelas Masih Kosong</h3>
          <p class="text-[14px] max-w-[450px]">Sistem tidak menemukan materi berformat teks atau HTML (Page/Label) di kelas Moodle Anda. Silakan isi materi di LMS Moodle Anda terlebih dahulu.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="materials-grid" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 hidden pb-24">
           </div>
      </div>

      <div id="preview-drawer" class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-full md:w-[450px] h-full bg-surface-card border-l border-hairline shadow-2xl transform translate-x-full transition-transform duration-300 flex flex-col z-20">
        <div class="p-5 border-b border-hairline flex justify-between items-center bg-surface-strong">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-ink">Preview Ekstraksi Teks</h4>
          <button type="button" id="btn-close-drawer" class="text-muted hover:text-ink"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i> Tutup</button>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 overflow-y-auto flex-1 text-[14px] text-body leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-wrap font-mono bg-canvas-soft" id="preview-drawer-content"></div>
      </div>

      <div id="wizard-step-2" class="w-full h-full overflow-y-auto p-10 bg-canvas hidden flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
        <div id="chunking-progress" class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 border-4 border-hairline-strong border-t-primary rounded-full animate-spin mx-auto mb-6"></div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-ink mb-2">Memproses Chunking...</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Mengekstrak teks, membuang struktur HTML, dan memotong materi ke database.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="chunking-success" class="hidden w-full max-w-lg bg-surface-card p-8 rounded-[16px] border border-semantic-success shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#ecfccb] text-semantic-success rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mx-auto mb-4"><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i></div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-center text-ink mb-6">Chunking Selesai</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-[14px] text-body mb-8" id="sync-summary-list"></ul>
          <button type="button" class="btn-close-modal w-full bg-primary text-white py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-primary-active">Selesai</button>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div id="wizard-footer" class="p-5 border-t border-hairline bg-surface-card flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center shrink-0 hidden gap-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <select id="sync-class-selector" class="bg-canvas border border-hairline-strong rounded-[8px] px-3 py-2 text-[14px] text-ink focus:outline-none w-40">
            <option value="ALL">Semua Kelas</option>
            <option value="8A">8A</option>
            <option value="8B">8B</option>
            <option value="8C">8C</option>
            <option value="8D">8D</option>
            <option value="8E">8E</option>
            <option value="8F">8F</option>
            <option value="8G">8G</option>
            <option value="8H">8H</option>
        </select>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="checkbox" id="reset-moodle-chunks" checked class="w-4 h-4 text-primary rounded border-hairline">
          <span class="text-[13px] text-body">Ganti data lama</span>
        </label>
      </div>
      <button type="button" id="btn-start-chunking" class="w-full md:w-auto bg-ink text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-[15px] font-medium hover:bg-surface-dark shadow-sm">
        Mulai Chunking <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
